# StatScreen is frontend-only by default — no env vars are required to run or
# deploy. Saved screenings live in the browser's localStorage.
#
# OPTIONAL: only if you later add a backend and want the UI to use it instead of
# localStorage. Set this at BUILD time (e.g. in Lovable's project env) to the
# absolute origin of your API. Leave blank for localStorage mode.
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.example.com
